text: Pamphinette "Pam" Buisa is a Canadian rugby sevens player. She won a gold medal at the 2019 Pan American Games as a member of the Canada women's national rugby sevens team. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Black Canadian sportspeople Category:Canada international rugby sevens players Category:Female rugby sevens players Category:Rugby sevens players at the 2019 Pan American Games Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Canada Category:Pan American Games medalists in rugby sevens Category:Sportspeople from Ottawa Category:Black Canadian women
